{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2016}} {{Use British English|date=June 2016}} {{italic title}} '''''The Diary of Anne Frank''''' is 1987 [[BBC]] televised miniseries. It was based on ''[[The Diary of a Young Girl]]'' by [[Anne Frank]], and it starred Elizabeth Bell, Janet Amsbury, [[Katharine Schlesinger]] and [[Emrys James]].
